# Tor + Proxychains Setup

## Installation

Make sure to install `tor` and `proxychains`. You can do this using the following commands:

```bash
sudo apt install tor proxychains
```

## Configuration

Edit the `proxychains` configuration file:

```bash
sudo nano /etc/proxychains.conf
```

Make sure to set the dynamic chain mode:

```plaintext
# dynamic_chain
```

## Starting Tor

To start Tor, use the following command:

```bash
sudo service tor start
```

## Running with Proxychains

To run a command with Proxychains, prepend `proxychains`:

```bash
proxychains curl ifconfig.me
```